column16: Mookie Betts doubles (9) on a sharp fly ball to center fielder Mallex Smith.   Christian Vazquez scores.
Mookie Betts grounds out, shortstop Adeiny Hechavarria to first baseman Brad Miller.
Mookie Betts flies out to left fielder Rob Refsnyder.
Christian Vazquez out at 2nd, catcher Wilson Ramos to second baseman Daniel Robertson.
Mookie Betts pops out to first baseman Brad Miller.
